OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772482267
OL,3,CMany will be apprehensive about Middle
OL,4,CEast tensions ` Little-Pengelly
OL,6,FMs Little-Pengelly was speaking after
OL,7,Freceiving a security briefing from a
OL,8,FUK Government adviser following US and
OL,9,FIsraeli forces' missile strikes on
OL,10,FIran on Saturday morning in what the
OL,11,Ftwo countries described as a "pre-
OL,12,Femptive" strike against a Tehran
OL,13,Fgovernment intent on developing
OL,14,Fnuclear weapons.
OL,16,FThe attack prompted retaliation from
OL,17,FIran, with missiles reported to have
OL,18,Ftargeted Israel and countries across
OL,19,Fthe Middle East.
OL,26,@sD@^OUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
