OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772482267
OL,3,CMany will be apprehensive about Middle
OL,4,CEast tensions ` Little-Pengelly
OL,6,FMs Little-Pengelly said: "I know that
OL,7,Fmany, many people will be really
OL,8,Fapprehensive about what is happening
OL,9,Fin Iran and across the Middle East.
OL,11,F"The Iranian regime is an appalling
OL,12,Fone, it has created a huge amount of
OL,13,Finstability in the region, it has
OL,14,Fkilled many thousands of its own
OL,15,Fcitizens.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772482267
OL,3,CMany will be apprehensive about Middle
OL,4,CEast tensions ` Little-Pengelly
OL,6,F"I know that there are many hundreds
OL,7,Fof people from Northern Ireland who
OL,8,Fare living and working in the Middle
OL,9,FEast, particularly in the UAE and of
OL,10,Fcourse many others that are visiting
OL,11,Fthe region as well.
OL,13,F"I know that there are a lot of people
OL,14,Fworried about their loved ones and
OL,15,Ffamilies at the moment."
OL,17,FThe deputy First Minister said the
OL,18,Fbriefing, which was also attended by
OL,19,Fthe Scottish and Welsh First
OL,20,FMinisters, was an opportunity to raise
OL,21,Fquestions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
