PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772482267
OL,3,CMany will be apprehensive about Middle
OL,4,CEast tensions ` Little-Pengelly
OL,6,FShe added: "Also to try to push to
OL,7,Fensure that the clear messages are
OL,8,Fcoming out from the UK Government,
OL,9,Fclear advice to people who are in the
OL,10,Fregion in terms of making sure that
OL,11,Fall of the support is there to keep
OL,12,Fpeople safe."
OL,14,FSDLP leader Claire Hanna said she was
OL,15,F"deeply concerned" about the situation.
OL,17,FShe said: "The UK must urgently push
OL,18,Ffor de-escalation, press for an
OL,19,Fimmediate ceasefire, and work with
OL,20,Finternational partners to prevent a
OL,21,Fwider war.
OL,26,@nD@LOUtD@MO]wD@AOUwD@RO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772482267
OL,3,CMany will be apprehensive about Middle
OL,4,CEast tensions ` Little-Pengelly
OL,6,F"Diplomacy, not further military
OL,7,Faction, must be the focus."
OL,9,FSinn Fein MP Chris Hazzard said the
OL,10,Fattacks on Iran "do nothing but bring
OL,11,Fthe threat of wider conflict in the
OL,12,FMiddle East closer".
OL,14,FHe added: "In the midst of ongoing
OL,15,Fnegotiations between the US and Iran,
OL,16,Fthese attacks are outrageous
OL,17,Fviolations of the United Nations
OL,18,FCharter and the multilateral system.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@[O]rD@QOUtD@SO]vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772482267
OL,3,CMany will be apprehensive about Middle
OL,4,CEast tensions ` Little-Pengelly
OL,6,F"This escalation must be condemned and
OL,7,Fthe attacks should end immediately
OL,8,Fwhile a return to negotiations must be
OL,9,Fa priority."
OL,11,FMr Hazzard added: "Many people from
OL,12,Fhere will be deeply worried about
OL,13,Ftheir loved ones living in the Middle
OL,14,FEast.
OL,16,F"I would encourage anyone concerned
OL,17,Fwho is living abroad or has families
OL,18,Foverseas to contact the Irish or
OL,19,FBritish Embassies for assistance."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]sD@SOUxD@AOU{D@bO]
